          <p class="skc-lead">
            The Skill Creator is Anthropic's own skill for <em>writing skills</em>. It asks you the right questions, writes the files, validates the trigger, and installs it. All while you talk in plain English.
          </p>
          <div class="skc-prompt">
              <div class="skc-prompt-head">
                <span class="skc-prompt-tag">The prompt →</span>
                <button class="skc-copy-btn" id="skc-copy-btn" type="button" aria-label="Copy prompt">
