              <pre class="skc-prompt-box" id="skc-prompt-text">Use the skill-creator skill to help me build a Skill.

I send an investor update on the last Friday of every month.
Same structure every time: cover · highlights · metrics ·
one surprise · one ask.

Interview me about my voice, format, and what "good" looks like.
Then draft the SKILL.md, a good example, and a template.</pre>
          </div>
        </div>
